92fff5f3-72c7-487d-9916-3102d5a2c55a.title: Juliet
92fff5f3-72c7-487d-9916-3102d5a2c55a.text:
Romeo, Romeo, wherefore art thou Romeo? Bold
adventurer, have you seen Romeo on your travels?
Skinny guy, a bit wishy washy, head full of poetry.

options.text: No, I think I'd have remembered if I'd met him.
ÈÅ∞ I guess I could look for him for you.
I think you could do better than Romeo!

7f92645f-4aa1-46ef-94e8-065391e6e24a.title: <player>
7f92645f-4aa1-46ef-94e8-065391e6e24a.text: Yes I've met him. He seemed a bit depressed.

13d879cc-a00a-43fa-9897-528b128a834a.title: Juliet
13d879cc-a00a-43fa-9897-528b128a834a.text:
Yes, that sounds like Romeo. I'd be very grateful if
you could deliver a message to him?

options.text: Certainly, I'll do so straight away.
No, he was a little too weird for me.

7fc65680-54da-495f-99f1-814091eb06a9.title: <player>
7fc65680-54da-495f-99f1-814091eb06a9.text: Certainly, I'll do so straight away.

143740fa-e6a9-48d4-8a11-c8859a9cc908.title: Juliet
143740fa-e6a9-48d4-8a11-c8859a9cc908.text:
Many thanks! Oh, I'm so very grateful. You may be
our only hope.

48949167-2ca1-400d-a1da-5fee2b498565.title: <player>
48949167-2ca1-400d-a1da-5fee2b498565.text: No, I think I'd have remembered if I'd met him.

09fe6dc3-87e7-4b2e-8348-951b1824ae70.title: Juliet
09fe6dc3-87e7-4b2e-8348-951b1824ae70.text:
Oh, well that's a shame, I was hoping that you might
deliver a message to him for me.

bfe62d07-66b9-4621-99ef-592d5a2b5963.title: <player>
bfe62d07-66b9-4621-99ef-592d5a2b5963.text:
Sorry, but I don't even know what he looks like or
where he is?

33a4dda9-8bc2-4c13-9b95-e701dd5a92f8.title: Juliet
33a4dda9-8bc2-4c13-9b95-e701dd5a92f8.text:
Oh, he's so lovely...in his own soppy and confused way.
You should spot him easily! He's usually fending off the
advances of the Varrockian market women. Are you
sure I couldn't persuade you to deliver my itsy bitsty

options.text: Certainly, I will do so straight away.
No, sorry, I have better things to do.

5252266c-e69e-46eb-963c-f49712d37709.title: <player>
5252266c-e69e-46eb-963c-f49712d37709.text: No, sorry, I have better things to do.

4d128bf4-8d96-4b01-857d-46c1fb61c5b7.title: Juliet
4d128bf4-8d96-4b01-857d-46c1fb61c5b7.text:
Then, I will not keep you from them.
Goodbye.

7101299a-6b86-44b4-84a6-eb1413df5e75.title: <player>
7101299a-6b86-44b4-84a6-eb1413df5e75.text: No, he was a little too weird for me.

c07b6973-87a1-4ef1-bcda-7f5f7a611eca.title: Juliet
c07b6973-87a1-4ef1-bcda-7f5f7a611eca.text:
Oh dear, that will be the ruin of our love. Well, I will
just stay here and worry. You unromantic soul.

4ae24f3e-4519-46a8-bdaa-f99ae01a9d01.title: <player>
4ae24f3e-4519-46a8-bdaa-f99ae01a9d01.text: I think you could do better than Romeo!

8c8cf1ae-3ae3-4374-9f8f-da44f5d15fe4.title: Juliet
8c8cf1ae-3ae3-4374-9f8f-da44f5d15fe4.text:
He has his good points, he's not obsessed with fighting,
magic and ranging at least.

80c16c4d-d413-4a7b-a1d3-a3cd5769c303.title: Juliet
80c16c4d-d413-4a7b-a1d3-a3cd5769c303.text:
He's a very different sort of man. Even if he is a bit
confused and soppy, he's my confused and soppy lover,
and I wait patiently until we're together.

91872741-1cd0-48b4-b810-298d1e6ce5c4.title: <player>
91872741-1cd0-48b4-b810-298d1e6ce5c4.text: I guess I could look for him for you.

40e5abd9-c6cd-4bee-ba26-63dfc8f3ea5d.title: Juliet
40e5abd9-c6cd-4bee-ba26-63dfc8f3ea5d.text:
Oh, that would be so wonderful of you! 
I'd be most grateful if you could please deliver a
message to him?

62f5c9e8-a734-4304-aea8-9eecbb54b99e.title: <player>
62f5c9e8-a734-4304-aea8-9eecbb54b99e.text:
Juliet, I come from Romeo. 
He begs me to tell you that he cares still.

ef3070f0-1ca9-4d15-989d-a3d12a013a55.title: Juliet
ef3070f0-1ca9-4d15-989d-a3d12a013a55.text:
Oh how my heart soars to hear this news! Please take
this message to him with great haste.

d7a86260-b9b1-4d15-bc00-d2d80633257d.title: <player>
d7a86260-b9b1-4d15-bc00-d2d80633257d.text:
Well, I hope it's good news...he was quite upset when I
left him.

5205c262-5845-4c27-af17-0a011cfa0013.title: Juliet
5205c262-5845-4c27-af17-0a011cfa0013.text:
He's quite often upset...the poor sensitive soul. But I
don't think he's going to take this news very well,
however, all is not lost.

07a07c2d-8ad7-498a-9971-d476113e8d54.title: Juliet
07a07c2d-8ad7-498a-9971-d476113e8d54.text:
Everything is explained in the letter, would you be so
kind and deliver it to him please?

8bbf1deb-784a-415c-8bbd-863fdc8f2c33.title: <player>
8bbf1deb-784a-415c-8bbd-863fdc8f2c33.text: Certainly, I'll do so straight away.

7ae0e25c-9fff-415a-9389-7b4fb9d26f69.title: Juliet
7ae0e25c-9fff-415a-9389-7b4fb9d26f69.text:
Many thanks! Oh, I'm so very grateful. You may be
our only hope.

98ebe613-5002-47cd-a896-121863e46a65.title: Juliet
98ebe613-5002-47cd-a896-121863e46a65.text:
Hello there...have you delivered the message to Romeo
yet? What news do you have from my loved one?

1b99f8d7-3d7f-40aa-8524-07c08015be8c.title: <player>
1b99f8d7-3d7f-40aa-8524-07c08015be8c.text: Oh, sorry, I've not had chance to deliver it yet!

150ee56c-3ad0-40f4-8dee-386c92eddf29.title: Juliet
150ee56c-3ad0-40f4-8dee-386c92eddf29.text:
Oh, that's a shame. I've been waiting so patiently to
hear some word from him.

b46a0e5b-bd51-4928-98c7-4b5774cef3cc.title: <player>
b46a0e5b-bd51-4928-98c7-4b5774cef3cc.text:
Hi Juliet, I've found Father Lawrence and he has a
cunning plan. But for it to work, I need to seek the
Apothecary!

c5e95328-9d5f-406e-809e-df039b62d780.title: Juliet
c5e95328-9d5f-406e-809e-df039b62d780.text:
Oh good! I knew Father Lawrence would come up with
something. However, I don't know where the apothecary
is...I hope you find him soon. My father's temper gets
no better.

aa1c473e-3249-4923-8835-db7e2e7a9b0f.title: <player>
aa1c473e-3249-4923-8835-db7e2e7a9b0f.text:
Hi Juliet! I have an interesting proposition for
you...suggested by Father Lawrence. It may be the
only way you'll be able to escape from this house and
be with Romeo.

db43f2bd-238e-4b9f-b539-87f922c74d30.title: <player>
db43f2bd-238e-4b9f-b539-87f922c74d30.text:
I have a Cadava potion here, suggested by Father
Lawrence. If you drink it, it will make you appear dead!

ce95bc15-6a9d-472a-8301-69e7d69e88d1.title: <player>
ce95bc15-6a9d-472a-8301-69e7d69e88d1.text:
And when you appear dead...your still and lifeless
corpse will be removed to the crypt!

7c8eb40d-0980-4fd4-bdc2-4b915e549c57.title: Juliet
7c8eb40d-0980-4fd4-bdc2-4b915e549c57.text: Oooooh, a cold dark creepy crypt...

005bb8d4-34e6-4fed-80ac-cd983544cb5b.title: <player>
005bb8d4-34e6-4fed-80ac-cd983544cb5b.text:
Then...Romeo can steal into the crypt and rescue you
just as you wake up!

f751064d-e94e-494d-9237-09d9f03a60c6.title: Juliet
f751064d-e94e-494d-9237-09d9f03a60c6.text: ...and this is the great idea for getting me out of here?

c0944313-c74f-4f2d-b5f4-2aed1f0f7c34.title: <player>
c0944313-c74f-4f2d-b5f4-2aed1f0f7c34.text:
To be fair, I can't take all the credit...in fact...it was all
Father Lawrence's suggestion...

2c6cc669-800f-41e7-9e97-3f6277bb012e.title: Juliet
2c6cc669-800f-41e7-9e97-3f6277bb012e.text: Ok...if this is the best we can do...hand over the potion!

691632eb-7afe-4325-a005-fa357d3882ad.text: You pass the suspicious potion to Juliet.

77a888d5-8ec2-4983-a7bd-2594a004da21.title: Juliet
77a888d5-8ec2-4983-a7bd-2594a004da21.text:
Wonderful! I just hope Romeo can remember to get
me from the crypt.

d2d07df8-0e59-4ccb-943f-96589bfa7547.title: Juliet
d2d07df8-0e59-4ccb-943f-96589bfa7547.text:
Please go to Romeo and make sure he understands.
Although I love his gormless, lovelorn soppy ways, he
can be a bit dense sometimes and I don't want to wake
up in that crypt on my own.

51f0c093-ec26-4c64-bea8-2f104ed68471.title: Juliet
51f0c093-ec26-4c64-bea8-2f104ed68471.text: Oh, here's Phillipa, my cousin...she's in on the plot too!

09c59c3b-55ca-4b11-9836-3dc6eaf44fa8.title: Juliet
09c59c3b-55ca-4b11-9836-3dc6eaf44fa8.text: She's going to make it seem even more convincing!

848c3139-40b4-4d20-8417-00b1eff059be.title: Phillipa
848c3139-40b4-4d20-8417-00b1eff059be.text: Yes, I'm quite the actress! Good luck dear cousin!

4b29b493-6a68-4ac8-a780-ace1c6a22276.title: <player>
4b29b493-6a68-4ac8-a780-ace1c6a22276.text:
You might be more believable if you're not smiling when
you say it...

bd834cac-317c-4617-a2f4-c40cc86987cc.title: Phillipa
bd834cac-317c-4617-a2f4-c40cc86987cc.text: Oh yeah...you might be right...ok, let's try again.

266c9b0b-ddcf-4a7b-b867-ced139a8e074.title: <player>
266c9b0b-ddcf-4a7b-b867-ced139a8e074.text:
Perhaps a bit louder, like you're upset...that your cousin
has died!

6a6526f3-93e1-4c48-950f-705f8fd20b4b.title: Phillipa
6a6526f3-93e1-4c48-950f-705f8fd20b4b.text:
Right...yes...Ok, ok, I think I'm getting my motivation
now. Ok, let's try this again!

f8003450-3813-4d9d-926c-cdc2b067619e.title: Phillipa
f8003450-3813-4d9d-926c-cdc2b067619e.text:
OH NO...JULIET HAS...DIED?....
Oooooohhhhhh....(sob), (sob).Juliet...my poor dead cousin!

1bac99d5-fadc-4144-bec9-d3b3e9dbe8b6.title: Draul Leptoc
1bac99d5-fadc-4144-bec9-d3b3e9dbe8b6.text: Oh no! My poor daughter...what has become of you?

c297d218-4cec-4832-91ca-326437b7e6eb.title: Phillipa
c297d218-4cec-4832-91ca-326437b7e6eb.text:
Poor Juliet...make preparations for her body to be
placed in the Crypt...
